I'm not going to put this off any longer, Casey.
我不能再拖了，凯西。

42
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:05,280
I want those photos ASAP.
我马上要那些照片。

43
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:10,040
All right.
好吧。

44
