那么，埃里卡，什么是截止日期？

54
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:37,120
It is the last possible date to do something.
就是做某事的最后可能日期。

55
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:40,640
So for example, when we were in school, our teacher would send us homework and say it
比如，我们上学时，老师布置作业会说

56
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:41,940
was for Friday.
周五交。

57
00:02:41,940 --> 00:02:43,480
